---
import Card from '../components/ui/Card.astro';
---

<section id="soluciones" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-bg-base">
  <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto text-center mb-20 reveal">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-text-main mb-6" data-i18n-key="solutions.title">
        Nuestro enfoque
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-text-muted">No vendemos webs. Construimos sistemas digitales que trabajan por ti las 24 horas del día.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <Card hoverEffect class="p-8 md:p-12 reveal">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-[16px] flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m12 14 4-4"/><path d="M3.34 19a10 10 0 1 1 17.32 0"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-main mb-4">Diseño de Autoridad</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Tu primera impresión importa. Creamos identidades visuales e interfaces "Silicon Valley Premium" que inspiran confianza instantánea en tus clientes.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-text-main">
            <svg class="text-success w-5 h-5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            Diseño minimalista y limpio
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-text-main">
            <svg class="text-success w-5 h-5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            Rendimiento extremo (Lighthouse 100)
          </li>
        </ul>
      </Card>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <Card hoverEffect class="p-8 md:p-12 reveal" style="transition-delay: 100ms;">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-[16px] flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2v20"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-main mb-4">Automatización</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Elimina cuellos de botella. Automatizamos tus reservas, presupuestos y respuestas de WhatsApp para que tú te enfoques en gestionar.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-text-main">
            <svg class="text-success w-5 h-5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            Chatbots de WhatsApp
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-text-main">
            <svg class="text-success w-5 h-5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            Sistemas de reservas nativos
          </li>
        </ul>
      </Card>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <Card hoverEffect class="p-8 md:p-12 reveal" style="transition-delay: 200ms;">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-[16px] flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-main mb-4">Crecimiento</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Haz que sea más fácil encontrarte. Optimizamos tu presencia para que Google te convierta en la opción preferida de tu zona.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-text-main">
            <svg class="text-success w-5 h-5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            SEO Local Avanzado
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-text-main">
            <svg class="text-success w-5 h-5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            Análisis y conversión
          </li>
        </ul>
      </Card>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
